Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:53.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How beautiful you must have been\nwhen you were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Midoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it that beauty that\ngave you the power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to create the Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Said to give powerto those who\npossess it and grant theirevery wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was from that time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:30.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to search forthe shards\nof the Sacred Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that ourjourney began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We continue ourpursuit of Naraku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who possesses most of\nthe Sacred Jewel shards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The breeze feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We haven't found a single\nclue to Naraku's whereabouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And here you are,\nwasting time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And because of Naraku's disappearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all sorts of demons who have\nlain low all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,are coming out of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust want to be able to\nenjoy my meal at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grow up a little, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unlike us powerful demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, Sango and Miroku\nare weak mortals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't ask for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did he call us "weak mortals"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:34.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It helps that Shippo is\nso mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Did I say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's the "powerful demon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just wake me when\nyou're done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:57.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... the air feels great\nand the riceball is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Such nice weather!\N- And fine weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I may be imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I feel something...\nlike the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can't you be more\nsure of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Overthat way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:32.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave 'im to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- You're safe now.\N- Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:51.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the big idea, runt?\NTrying to interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he the one, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. He has a Sacred Jewel\nshard in his belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So where'd you get\nthis Jewel shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you know about\nmy Sacred Jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you'd betterhand over\nthat fellow quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you leave that\NJewel shard here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and {\i1}quietly{\i0} get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impudent kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Know the might of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing to brag about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ridiculous... this isn't supposed\nto happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:38.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha shattered\nthe Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! The Sacred Jewel\nwouldn't break so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:57.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I sensed the same presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an imitation Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:06.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a demon trying to\nduplicate the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but may I\nhave a drink of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,such a beautiful water container.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just who is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My family has served as\n{\i1}guujifor{\i0} centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guuji?{\i0} What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:46.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are shrine keepers.\NLike my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see! That's why you\nare a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I began my studies in order\nto better serve the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I became engrossed\nin scholarship
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:01.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and traveled to many countries\nto learn, research and record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell us about the\nimitation Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The purpose of my studies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is precisely to learn about\nthe Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why you know\nabout its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the universe, everything in life,\nis created from four spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aramitama, Nigimitama,\NKushimitama{\i0} and {\i1}Sakimitama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When these four spirits are in synthesis,\nthey become one,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and in the human body\nbecomes the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are we going back to that again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that before,\nbut I neverreally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:43.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Explain how that demon\ngot possession of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the fake Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because someone gave\nit to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You looking for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, ljust...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why was that demon\nchasing you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:03.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's because\NI saw the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that there was a shrine which\ntold the legend of the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I made my way\nto the mountain path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buteventually, I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I came upon a demon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,handing the Sacred Jewel\nto that demon you just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was he called Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No. He called himself Orochidayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he said that the Jewel was\nnot yet complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but that soon a true Sacred\NJewel would be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're saying that a demon\nis making Sacred Jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all I overheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense any presence\nof demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was just around here\nthat I witnessed that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't catch any scent\nof Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like\nhe's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you sense the presence\nof the Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like it's a\nstrong presence to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Cuz it's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It probably doesn't\nwork that well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say! There's a village\noverthere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not a sign of anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Word has it that this shrine\nhouses the Deity of Origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:56.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is the Deity of Origin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a legend that says\nfrom the heart of this Deity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:07.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,were born the spirits\N{\i1}Kushimitama{\i0} and {\i1}Sakimitama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kushimitama{\i0} which embodies\N{\i1}Chi{\i0} (knowledge)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and {\i1}Sakimitama{\i0} which\nembodies {\i1}Ai{\i0} (love).
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:18.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aramitama{\i0} symbolizes {\i1}Yu{\i0} (courage) and\N{\i1}Nigimitama{\i0} symbolizes {\i1}Shin{\i0} (friendship).
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yu, Shin, Chi, Ai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:24.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are the four spirits\nof the Shikon Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh! I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind such talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm getting a weird feeling\nfrom this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should investigate\na bit deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll check the\nvillage outskirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:42.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We haven't found a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is the sun so warm\nand blinding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only natural that\nthe sun is blinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's wondrous to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:03.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something burning\noveryonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore, just how far\nis it to the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He thinks up such\nweird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:16.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... I've nevermet a man\nwho thinks like he does in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:17.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it common in\nyourworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why does night fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo is a scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About the four spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}Yu{\i0} and {\i1}Shin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:40.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, {\i1}Yu, Shin, Chi, Ai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yu{\i0} means courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand when you\nexplain it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shin{\i0} means friendship...\nto be intimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:56.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chimeans knowledge...\nto know things well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ai{\i0} is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something-mitama...\nor whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand\nthatgibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aramitama{\i0} of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nigimitama{\i0} of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kushimitama{\i0} of knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakimitama{\i0} of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you gather these\nfour spirits into one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And when good and evil are\nsealed amidst chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then it is possible for\na Sacred Jewel to be created.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Again, I'm lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Sango's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't do a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will not harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay away, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:13:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neither Shippo nor\NKirara are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did something happen\nin this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:15.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever happened,\nwe'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons came and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did demons attack\nthe village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was punished forbeing\nnaughty and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:32.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,put in the chicken coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on out quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'll burn you alive\nin yourhomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa! Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every single one of\nyou must come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is anyone hiding?\NFind them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:09.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone was taken away\nby the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About five days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been hiding in the coop\never since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So now we know why\nthe village is deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:24.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did the demons take\NPa and Ma away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:37.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were they eaten up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they only came to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they wouldn't have taken\nthem all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe they've\nbeen eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons aren't fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They know that\nif they attack villages ruthlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,people would hire\ndemon slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they took them alive,\nthere's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Pa and Ma are\nstill alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll go find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we'll slay the demons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you! I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will be night soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope we can find\ntheirwhereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:28.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hides everything in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the most beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is covered by the\ndarkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I sensed the\npresence of mortals...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but to come upon\nreal Sacred Jewel shards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons who kidnapped\nmy parents and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand overthe Sacred Jewel\nshards quietly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the ones who\nshould be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Orochidayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did you take\nthe villagers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk... I've heard rumors\nabout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one with the Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, if you're aware of it,\nit'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, will you behave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seems this Sacred Jewel\nis a cluster of noxious vapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's probably toxic\nto humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Jewel will defile\nthe human soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They all possess fake\NSacred Jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:07.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo, take the boy\nand hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're strongerthan\nthe average demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:39.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though it's an imitation,\ncould it be the Sacred Jewel's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how did they make\nsuch a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time to\nworry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use my Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't know this\nwould be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsuchigumo! Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think that swallowing a\nfake Jewel will make you strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Release us!\N- Leggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Izumo!\N- Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:31.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind... Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The others got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Overthere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:33.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Delicious-looking souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you eat any of them,\NGamajiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remove this kid's soul, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa! Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll soon join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gyu-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:00.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, we shall see your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's this way, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... this place reeks of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think it's straight ahead\nin this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I can't sense that\NSacred Jewel too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can feel the Sacred Jewel\ncoming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're all fake Sacred Jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come at me, you foolish half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what if I'm...\na half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Atoxic miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get too cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the Wind Scar didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess with the\NSacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The human soul must be polished, too.\NOtherwise, it's just a mere pebble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does he mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My mothernamed me Gyu-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's all yourdoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:54.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You tricked us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:55.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:57.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your soul and the Sacred Jewel\nshards will become
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:23:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the basis of a real Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:24:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But they are notenough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is why I mustgather\na supply of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will use the power of the\NSacred Jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.60,0:24:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to free myself from this destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Sacred Jewel Maker, Part Il"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.37,0:24:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall possess all things beautiful\nin this world!
